<HEAD>`Beverly Hills Cop' Reinhold In Fender Bender</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LIGHTHOUSE POINT, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   As an actor in both ``Beverly
Hills Cop'' movies, Judge Reinhold is no stranger to car crashes.
   But Reinhold, 31, was in a real _ although minor _ car accident
Tuesday. Police say Reinhold, whose real first name is Edward, was
rear-ended by a car driven by Hugo Silsby, 19, of Deerfield Beach.
   Reinhold's rented 1988 Ford Mustang had to be towed from the
