   Silsby was ticketed for failing to use due care. Reinhold, a Los
Angeles resident, complained at the scene of minor neck and back
injuries but refused treatment, police said.
   The actor was taken to police headquarters to arrange a ride to
the home of friends living in Palm Beach County.
