<HEAD>Costello Wins Special Primary</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BELLEVILLE, Ill. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Jerry Costello won a special Democratic
primary and will face Republican Robert Gaffner in August for the
right to serve out the remaining months of the late Melvin Price's
term in Congress.
   Costello, chairman of the St. Clair County Board, on Tuesday
overwhelmed East St. Louis Alderman Clarence Ellis Sr., 18,259
