others, or strikes out against injustice, he sends forth a tiny
ripple of hope, and crossing each other from a million different
centers of energy and of daring, those ripples build a current
which can sweep down the mightiest walls of oppression and of
resistance.'' My friends, the future of America doesn't depend on
some nameless, outside force, and it certainly doesn't depend on
the alignment of the stars, the future depends on us. The future
depends on us.
