<1ST_LINE>a e BC-WeekendTV-Scott Adv22-24   07-13 0761</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>BC-Weekend TV-Scott, Adv 22-24,0779</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>$Adv22</NOTE>
<NOTE>$Adv23</NOTE>
